### 🔐 **Security & Compliance**
✅ **Implemented:**
- Row-Level Security (RLS) on all tables
- AES-256-GCM token encryption for OAuth credentials
- Rate limiting (distributed via Upstash/Vercel KV)
- CSRF protection (httpOnly cookies for OAuth state)
- Input validation via Zod schemas
- OWASP compliance (CSP headers, X-Frame-Options, etc.)

⚠️ **Audit Findings** (from CLAUDE.md):
- 18 deduction engine findings (entertainment FBT, instant asset write-off thresholds, base rate entity test)
- 5 Division 7A findings (hardcoded interest rate, minimum repayment formula gaps)
- 7 loss engine findings (capital loss distinction, Similar Business Test incomplete)
- 5 trust distribution findings (Section 100A exclusions, trustee penalty rate)

---

### 🤖 **AI & Agent System**
**Multi-Agent Architecture:**
- **Framework Agents (Development):** Orchestrator + 4 Specialists (Architect, Developer, Tester, Reviewer)
- **Tax Domain Agents (32 agents):** R&D, Deduction, Loss, Division 7A, Trust, CGT, FBT, PSI, Payroll Tax, Superannuation, etc.
- **Skills Registry:** 22 reusable skills (tax law research, Xero API, rate scraping, report generation, etc.)
- **Workflows:** 22 orchestrated workflows (tax-audit, rnd-assessment, bad-debt-scan, business-transition, etc.)

**AI Models:**
- Primary: Google Gemini 3-Flash (1M token context, multimodal)
- Fallbacks: Gemini 2.5-Flash, Gemini 2.5-Pro
- Rate: 15 req/min (free tier), exponential backoff

